From 967ff09b28c64cedc996fd70273b65f4cd709a65 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nyd Iokar <nydiokar@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 15:10:58 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add HMAC-authenticated flow decision feed endpoint
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

GET /flow/dry-run/decisions returns a bounded, agent-readable JSON feed
of recent dry-run decisions sourced from the execution journal DB.

Gated by verifyHmac (WEBHOOK_SECRET) — same protection as /signal.
Stable fields: decision_id, token_ref, decision_status, risk_decision,
blocker_codes, source, created_at, live_execution_enabled=false.
Sensitive DB columns (raw_payload_json, normalized_signal_json,
lease_owner, journal_path, risk_config_json, risk_checks_json,
idempotency_key) are never included in the response.
blocker_codes only populated when risk_decision=rejected; error and
accepted states always emit [].

7 fixture-backed tests covering auth rejection, redaction, blocker
semantics, and limit param.
